      "title": "Litro is profitable",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The company states that Litro made a profit of over 7000 lakh rupees in August. Also in July the company had become profitable.",
        "Meanwhile, the company mentions that the price of a liter gas cylinder will be reduced by 100-200 rupees tomorrow."
